### Variables
@base_url = http://localhost:8000

### Health Check
GET {{base_url}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Upload Single Text File
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="hello.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello, World!
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Upload Single JSON File
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="data.json"
Content-Type: application/json

{"key": "value", "nested": {"a": 1}}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Upload Multiple Files
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="doc1.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

First document content
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="doc2.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Second document content
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Upload with Collection
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="notes.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Collection-bound content
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="collection"

my-research-papers
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Upload with Metadata
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="report.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

(dummy PDF content)
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="metadata"

{"author": "John Doe", "department": "engineering", "priority": "high"}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Upload with Collection and Metadata
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="full-example.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Full example with both collection and metadata
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="collection"

knowledge-base
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="metadata"

{"source": "manual", "version": 1}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--
